00:36:11.090 --> 00:36:12.670
there is little malaria.

00:36:12.670 --> 00:36:16.580
People are more likely to get
bed nets at any price--

00:36:16.580 --> 00:36:20.240
the red dots are for
the same price--

00:36:20.240 --> 00:36:24.010
at any price, people will be
more likely to get bed nets in

00:36:24.010 --> 00:36:27.110
the high-malaria region than
